Package: data.tree
Type: Package
Title: data.tree is to hierarchical data whata data.frame is to tabular data.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-01-06
Author: Christoph Glur
Maintainer: Christoph Glur <christoph.glur@ipub.ch>
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:
    R6
Suggests:
    testthat, magrittr, knitr
Description: Create tree structures from hierarchical data, and use the utility methods to traverse the tree in various orders and to aggregate. Print, convert from and to data.frame, and apply functions to your tree data.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://github.com/gluc/data.tree
BugReports: http://github.com/gluc/data.tree/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
